properties.description: Insurance mapping from pre dim risk object

typeProperties.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> Ica
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> ina
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> paa
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> peb
source(output(
		PK_KEY as string,
		CPT_DESCRIPTION as string,
		CPT_NUMBER as integer,
		INSERTED_BY as string,
		DATE_INSERTED as date
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> tcross
peb select(skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtable
peb select(skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtable1
